                <h1>FMCSA Background Check Requirements for CDL Drivers</h1>
                <p>The FMCSA requires thorough background checks for all commercial driver's license (CDL) holders to ensure public safety. Key requirements include checking driving history, criminal records, and prior employment in the transportation sector. These checks help identify disqualifying offenses such as drug abuse or serious traffic violations.</p>
